headline: Social media goes on trial in LA - here's what you need to know
summary: Inside LA's superior court, a landmark trial is getting under way.  Opening statements for the first lawsuit will start on Monday, with Meta chief executive Mark Zuckerberg among the tech execs expected to testify.  Over the years, people have tried to sue the owners of Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, TikTok and Snapchat for online harm, but they've largely failed.
